@ClubsApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5084
@AuthToken = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Auth - Register (student)
POST {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@bugbusters.dev",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

### Auth - Login
POST {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@bugbusters.dev",
  "password": "Student123!"
}

### Clubs - Options
GET {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/clubs/options

### Clubs - List
GET {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/clubs?page=1&pageSize=9

### Clubs - Detail
GET {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/clubs/1

### Events - List
GET {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/events?page=1&pageSize=10

### Events - Detail
GET {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/events/1

### Event Registration (student)
POST {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/events/1/registrations
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

### Club Membership Apply (student)
POST {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/clubs/1/applications
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "note": "Ba≈üvuruyorum"
}

### SKS Club Applications (club admin submit)
POST {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/sks/club-applications
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clubId": 1
}

### SKS Club Applications (sks admin list)
GET {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/sks/club-applications?status=Pending
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

### SKS Event Documents (sks admin list)
GET {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/sks/event-documents?status=Pending
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

### Admin Stats (sks admin)
GET {{ClubsApi_HostAddress}}/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
